{"tid":858980,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[女SOLO最初~] IU奧運會場 2場演唱會 1分鐘11577席全售罄!","createTime":"2018-10-12T07:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T13:32:03.000Z","uid":34643,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6dcdc6710324ddeac81a43eaefdcbeb519419c","tid":858980,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:43:26.000Z","msg":"橫掃音源榜單的IU,單獨演唱會門票也全席售罄,正在書寫著不斷的&quot;新記錄&quot;.<br />\n<br />\n12日,IU所屬社方面表示&quot;紀念IU出道10周年亞洲巡迴演唱會繼釜山-光州之後直至首爾,在全國3個城市的4場演唱會門票全部售罄.&quot;特別是在韓國時間11日晚8時進行的首爾場普通預售開始僅1分鐘就全部售罄,引發各方關注.據悉通過melon ticket購買此次演唱會門票的同時在線人數就達到了約5萬人.<br />\n<br />\n同時IU也是首位在首爾大規模公演場的奧林匹克體操競技場舉辦&quot;兩場次&quot;單獨演唱會的KPOP女solo.<br />\n<br />\n另一方面,IU於10月10日發表的10周年數碼單曲在韓國國內8個主要音源排行榜上取得了all kill的好成績,並在韓國最大音源網站Melon的累計音源用戶人數在發行僅一天就突破了146萬名,打破了Melon的&quot;歷代24小時最高使用者人數新記錄&quot;.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uCuuRzh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuCuuRzh.gif&h=75a0e2e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"709d94784390a0b6827bf645307168dac5fd2996","tid":858980,"uid":18156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/12/160810_0a6b3f0114b3b97988b407efaefffa76.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2F160810_0a6b3f0114b3b97988b407efaefffa76.gif&h=be1f48f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0353b5c86cdc596c995ccf2028ccb9b58ece5f0d","tid":858980,"uid":34643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"709d94784390a0b6827bf645307168dac5fd2996","tid":858980,"uid":18156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/12/160810_0a6b3f0114b3b97988b407efaefffa76.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2F160810_0a6b3f0114b3b97988b407efaefffa76.gif&h